arStrings.szText: Kurast is an old city. You've seen the gardens and the ziggurats, but there are many older places beneath our feet, places no one goes. The Undercity.
In good times, the Undercity is a bittersweet memory. These are not good times. People are going missing. We sent one of our own to investigateâ€”Councilor Sihek. Now he's gone missing himself.
Ormus wouldn't ask this of anyone else. Find Sihek for us. We fear for him.
